{
  "stem": "1282.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was beyond fear.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yes, fear was constant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But when you are-- when the fear is constant and you are ready to-- you know that you're going to get killed if you're caught, something strange happens.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You live with that fear.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How can I compare it to-- it's-- it's uncomparable to anything else.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I knew I would get killed instantly if I'm caught.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this was a mission.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was a kid, but this was my mission to-- I-- I volunteered for this.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some people didn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some people were selfish and hide out in the woods.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some people changed into Gentile papers and-- and befriended a Gentile family who took them in.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Some people joined churches.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everybody did whatever they could to survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was my choice.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was my choice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I lived with that fear, but not to the point where I become dysfunctional.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I functioned with fear, constantly with fear.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But I did not let fear stop me from doing what I believed in doing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I have to tell you some interesting little stories.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But there are thousands of them and we would take days to describe all of the daily happenings.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But, for example, we always had problems where to sleep, because by this time, I did not go back to the place where my mother found me this job, and I had no place to sleep at.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We slept in different places.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But if we slept in a place where we were exposed though, we were just machine-gunned.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We were shot down immediately, because death was not by trial.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That was, you're guilty, walk you to the Danube, tie one hand to another guy, because they wanted to save the bullet.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
